window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I took control of the Shadow Clan, giving the district's residents something they hadn't had in years—a chance to breathe freely. Independence, protection, and a shot at a normal life.</p> <p>But to the rest of society, the Shadow Clan was still nothing more than a den of killers, criminals, and thieves.</p> <p>They despised us. They refused to leave us alone. And worst of all? They underestimated us.</p> <p>A fatal mistake for the puppet masters who were determined to reclaim their lost toy—no matter the cost.</p>"; 
